com.unvired.chyme.api

Class SalesforceEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.unvired.chyme.api.SalesforceEvent

  • public class SalesforceEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    The SalesforceEvent class is an abstraction of a business event or trigger generated in Salesforce.com An event is the creation, updating or deletion of a business entity in Salesforce.com

    An event from Salesforce.com has the following components.

    • ID - Unique ID identifying an entity in Salesforce.com
    • Object - The entity in Salesforce.com generating the event
    • Old Value - A json representation of the old state of the entity in Salesforce.com before the event
    • New Value - A json representation of the new state of the entity in Salesforce.com after the event
